data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Jacksonville, NC. This property offers a range of features, making it a must-see. This home is roomy and inviting, with three bedrooms providing ample living space for your family. Enjoy a mix of laminate and carpet flooring throughout, creating a cozy and welcoming atmosphere. A spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinetry and counter space, making it a chef's dream. It's perfect for preparing meals and hosting family gatherings. Warm up on chilly evenings by the wood-burning fireplace in the living area, adding that touch of coziness and charm to the home. The backyard offers space for outdoor activities, gardening, or just relaxing with loved ones. Conveniently located in Jacksonville, NC, close to schools, shopping, dining, and other amenities. This home is move-in ready, allowing you to settle in with ease.
